00:36:20,830 --> 00:36:23,180
Exotic spices are major goods here,

764
00:36:23,880 --> 00:36:26,520
including storesin, benzoin,

765
00:36:26,630 --> 00:36:29,150
black tambac, dutchmanspipe root, and dalbergia benthamii.

