It is in a village

795
00:38:00,530 --> 00:38:01,610
17.5km outside the Mingde Gate.

796
00:38:03,540 --> 00:38:04,060
Get the horse ready.

797
00:38:05,090 --> 00:38:05,540
The Chang'an side also

