844
00:39:56,400 --> 00:39:56,800
I...

845
00:40:14,280 --> 00:40:14,790
Su Wuming.

846
00:40:16,980 --> 00:40:17,630
Su Wuming.

847
00:40:21,800 --> 00:40:22,680
