855
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:41,040
You're crazy.

856
00:40:46,050 --> 00:40:47,740
You inspire me.

857
00:40:48,500 --> 00:40:50,050
Wu Daqi must be

858
00:40:50,080 --> 00:40:50,870
crazy back then.

859
00:40:51,010 --> 00:40:51,780
Otherwise,

860
00:40:51,810 --> 00:40:53,050
